no-space-before-semi.description:
Description

This rule prevents the use of spaces before a semicolon in expressions.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

var foo = "bar" ;

var foo = function() {} ;

var foo = function() {
} ;

var foo = 1 + 2 ;

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

;(function(){}());

var foo = "bar";
